turbovncui (8.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Added TurboVNC username parameter support (-User flag)
  * Enhanced connection string handling for proper authentication
  * Added About dialog with version information and project details
  * Added About button to main interface
  * Added version display to status bar (right-justified)
  * Enhanced automatic TurboVNC detection
  * Improved compatibility with Ubuntu TurboVNC installations
  * Complete Debian package support

